INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (3,1,'2012-06-08 04:13:40','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2012-06-08 04:13:40','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.bloomboxphoto.com/blog/?p=3',0,'post','',0),(4,2,'2012-06-09 16:27:44','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2012-06-09 16:27:44','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.bloomboxphoto.com/blog/?p=4',0,'post','',0),(5,2,'2012-05-19 08:00:18','2012-05-19 12:00:18','Ever imagine attending your friend\'s wedding and actually got the honor to capture their happy moments? In the month of May, a lovely couple whom the bride is Carlos\' fiancee best friend were having their vow.  The ceremony was very traditional and it was definitely a fun and an intimate moments for all their family and guests.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://blog.bloomboxphoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Ciprian-+-Mahrukh-505.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-139\" title=\"Ciprian-+-Mahrukh-505\" src=\"http://blog.bloomboxphoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Ciprian-+-Mahrukh-505.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"853\" height=\"1280\" /></a></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nIt was such a great night for all of us to be able to see so much excitement from the couple and their friends engagement pictures\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.bloomboxphoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Ciprian-+-Mahrukh-209.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-141\" title=\"Ciprian-+-Mahrukh-280\" src=\"http://blog.bloomboxphoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Ciprian-+-Mahrukh-280.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" /><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-140\" title=\"Ciprian-+-Mahrukh-559\" src=\"http://blog.bloomboxphoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Ciprian-+-Mahrukh-559.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" /><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-138\" title=\"Ciprian-+-Mahrukh-209\" src=\"http://blog.bloomboxphoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Ciprian-+-Mahrukh-209.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe wedding was celebrated at Woodbine Banquet Convention Hall in Mississauga. We spent nearly half of the day having fun capturing their preparation. The hall was packed and the celebration was done in Islamic way.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.bloomboxphoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Ciprian-+-Mahrukh-116.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-29\" title=\"Ciprian and Mahrukh Wedding\" src=\"http://blog.bloomboxphoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Ciprian-+-Mahrukh-116.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"853\" height=\"1280\" /></a><a href=\"http://blog.bloomboxphoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Ciprian-+-Mahrukh-36.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-28\" title=\"Ciprian and Mahrukh Wedding\" src=\"http://blog.bloomboxphoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Ciprian-+-Mahrukh-36.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" /></a><a href=\"http://blog.bloomboxphoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Ciprian-+-Mahrukh-154.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-30\" title=\"Ciprian and Mahrukh Wedding\" src=\"http://blog.bloomboxphoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Ciprian-+-Mahrukh-154.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" /></a><a href=\"http://blog.bloomboxphoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Ciprian-+-Mahrukh-567.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-31\" title=\"Ciprian and Mahrukh Wedding\" src=\"http://blog.bloomboxphoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Ciprian-+-Mahrukh-567.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" /></a><a href=\"http://blog.bloomboxphoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Ciprian-+-Mahrukh-617.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-33\" title=\"Ciprian and Mahrukh Wedding\" src=\"http://blog.bloomboxphoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Ciprian-+-Mahrukh-617.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" /></a><a href=\"http://blog.bloomboxphoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Ciprian-+